text: What's up, Sakuyan? You seem in high spirits, huh?

In cute outfits that still make me a bit nervous when I'm alone,
and surrounded by adorable things during the shoot──
I feel like I can relax and have fun when I'm with everyone.

Nah, nah,
You don't have to be scared anymore, okay? Sakuyan──

──Alright!
Can we check the photos, please?
